    where \(\alpha\) is the [fine-structure constant](/Fine-structure_constant). This solution (using [substitutions](/Substitution_(algebra)) for quantum numbers) is equivalent to the solution of the [Dirac equation](/Dirac_equation). [11] Nevertheless, both solutions fail to predict the [Lamb shifts](/Lamb_shift).

